data.description: This beautiful NEW home is a must see. With 4 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, guest suite downstairs, loft and a beautiful open kitchen Dining and Great Room. The kitchen has a wonderful island and lots of cabinet space. This home has finished options that include upgraded cabinets, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, wood plank tile throughout the home downstairs, except for the bedrooms/den. This is a brand-new community with great access to the freeways, shopping and close to schools
